----------------
  libcam1394-0.1.2
----------------
add
 - support IplImage strucutre, which is one of IPL's image 
 structure. CopyIplImage(IplImage*) can copy image to IplImage
 structure directly
 - add document in doc directory.  These documents are generated
 by Doxygen
fix
 - fix some incorrect include path
 - correct libtool scripts, which cause to make illegal shared
 library in some distributions
